{"type": "article", "id": 2728, "title": "Ludovica模块化台灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-09T07:45:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232501rze1Val76mvAYyUd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t睡前翻翻书是不少都市人忙碌一天后的小习惯。近日，设计团队 ZANOCCHI &amp; STARKE 就为忙碌的都市人带来了一款造型简洁、使用方便的小台灯 Ludovica ，由一个 LED 灯以及一个梯形书立两部分组成，自然也提供照明与收纳整理书籍两种功能。此外，Ludovica 采用 USB 线进行充电，一次充满后可连续使用 5 个小时，方便移动不受限，应急时更可带到室外进行使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232458WD8vSMk1p0qygRot.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232458tZQqnRj3dN8xVSfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232459Q8YNJfvcVdO6GwhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232500HjZwcEM5XlsQh3nO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232500Dz8SWY5bqZLUxwpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}